subtests.name: The submit event must be fired when click a button in submit status
The reset event must be fired when click a button in reset status
type=button shouldn't trigger submit or reset events
Switching from type=button to type=submit should submit the form
Switching from type=button to type=reset should reset the form
Innermost button should submit its form
Innermost button should reset its form
Anchor inside a button should be prevent button activation
input type=submit inside a button should be prevent button activation
